6000|$|... "I do not know. He struck me, and I went mad. I {{have seen}} the apes of my tribe do the same thing. I have never told you my story, Olga. It {{would have been better}} had you known it--this might not have happened. <b>I</b> never <b>saw</b> <b>my</b> <b>father.</b> The only mother I knew was a ferocious she-ape. Until I was fifteen I had never seen a human being. I was twenty before <b>I</b> <b>saw</b> a white man. A {{little more than a year}} ago I was a naked beast of prey in an African jungle.|$|R
